title: Dr.wait - doctor's office.

creator: Dr.wait
descriptionHtml:
Wait for your next doctor's appointment with Dr.wait from home and don't waste time. Dr.wait is the practice app with the digital waiting room of the future. With this waiting room app, you always know exactly how long you have to wait and how many people are waiting in line in front of you. But this practice app can do much more.

If you just want to clarify something, you can of course also chat directly with the doctor's office without making a single call. Just pick up a prescription? No problem with Dr.wait.

This practice app with it's digital waiting room is a dream for the family doctor's practice. Your patients arrive on time and thanks to the automatic reminders, your patients will never forget their insurance card and referrals. With the waiting room manager you always have full control over the queue. You can also manage several rooms in a group practice at the same time.

Here's a rundown of the best features for doctor's offices:

✅ All patient data is encrypted.
✅ Manage up to 10 queues at the same time.
✅ Appointment management with online booking via the practice app for patients.
✅ Automated processes with workflows and events.
✅ Chat with your patients in the waiting room.
✅ Branding lets your patients wait even nicer.
✅ Reduce the risk of infection from crowded waiting rooms.
✅ Your patients book their doctor's appointments online directly in the practice app.

Dr.wait costs 19.90 EUR/month. The practice app is free for patients.

Register now on drwait.de and create your online waiting room easily and free of charge. Your patients will love you.

The practice app, including the digital waiting room, is great for patients. Before you even leave the house, you know exactly when it's your turn. From then on it's time to wait! You can use the time to go shopping or enjoy a little coffee around the corner. Time management has never been so easy. Dr.wait does not need to be registered. Every time you connect to your GP practice, your name is transmitted, which is only stored in the waiting room manager for a maximum of 24 hours. The messages in the chat are also deleted after a maximum of 24 hours. Data economy is a must in the practice app.

Here is an overview of the functions for patients:

✅ Always take your personal waiting time with you.
✅ See how many patients are still in front of you.
✅ Always be on time without waiting forever.
✅ Chat with the practice to clarify things in advance.
✅ Never forget your insurance card and transfer again.
✅ Book your appointments in 60 seconds directly in the practice app.
✅ Your data is encrypted.


-------------------------------------------------- -------------------------------------------------- ----------

Dr.wait, also sometimes spelled Dr wait or drwait, is an app for your doctor's office. The doctor's app, with waiting room, forms and online appointments, aims to eliminate waiting times. Practices in Germany, Austria and Switzerland can now create a practice app profile free of charge on drwait.de and individually manage their general practice with waiting room. For further questions and support, Dr.wait can be reached at business@drwait.de. The practice app is now available for download for Android and iOS.
